5) Kernel vs Shell
| Feature          | Kernel       | Shell      |
| ---------------- | ------------ | ---------- |
| Role             | Core of OS   | Interface  |
| Runs in          | Kernel space | User space |
| Hardware access  | Yes          | No         |
| User interaction | No           | Yes        |
| Crash impact     | Whole system | Only shell |
| Examples         | Process mgmt | bash, zsh  |

